    <item>
      <title>El Presidente</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/el-presidente/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2018 12:27:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/el-presidente/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1½ oz white rum&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz curaçao or orange liqueur&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz dry vermouth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;dash of grenadine&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;orange twist&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Stir all liquids with ice. Strain into a coupe glass. Garnish with orange twist.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
