    <item>
      <title>Martini</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/martini/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2018 11:30:58 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/martini/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;Everyone has an opinion about martinis. I’ll spare you mine, and just give you my recipe. Trust me.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I often use a blanc vermouth instead of the traditional dry, but it’s delicious with either. Any &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/ingredients/gin/&#34;&gt;type of gin&lt;/a&gt; works in a martini, but I prefer a sweeter style.&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2¼ oz genever gin&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz dry vermouth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Add to cocktail shaker with plenty of ice. Stir well, then strain into a martini glass.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Garnish with a lemon twist.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>French Kiss</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/french-kiss/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2018 12:21:43 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/french-kiss/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;As always, use only &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/ingredients/vermouth/#brands&#34;&gt;high quality vermouth&lt;/a&gt; that is &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/ingredients/vermouth/#storing-vermouth&#34;&gt;fresh&lt;/a&gt; (less than three months old).&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz sweet vermouth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz dry vermouth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Build in a rocks glass. Garnish with a lemon twist.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
